 pf-58_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-59_ pf-text-1"><strong>Autism Spectrum Disorder (ASD)</strong> - A developmental condition affecting social interaction, communication, and behaviour.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-61_ pf-text-1"><strong>Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD)</strong> - It is characterised by inattention, hyperactivity, and impulsivity.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-63_ pf-text-1"><strong>Dyslexia</strong> - A specific learning disability affecting reading and language processing.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-65_ pf-text-1"><strong>Dyspraxia</strong> - Impairments in motor coordination and planning.</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-4569" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-gjNHFA iojfsv pf-67_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1000px" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC"><div class="sc-pVTFL cZzoXH pf-68_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hjGZqJ dfjDDX pf-69_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Dyslexia_demystified_Facts_and_solutions_in_Liverpool_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1720597239" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Dyslexia_demystified_Facts_and_solutions_in_Liverpool_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1720597239 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Dyslexia_demystified_Facts_and_solutions_in_Liverpool_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1720597239 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Dyslexia demystified Facts and solutions in Liverpool - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Dyslexia demystified Facts and solutions in Liverpool - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-kYHfwS QlfnY pf-7